<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5260968>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Distribution map of species. a) Actinostola georgiana Carlgren, 1927. b) Hormosoma scotti Stephenson, 1918. c) Stomphia selaginella (Stephenson, 1918). d) Galatheanthemum profundale Carlgren, 1956. e) Actinoscyphia plebeia (McMurrich, 1893). f) Eltaninactis infundibulum Dunn, 1983. Green triangles, type locality; green circles, previous localities; red circles, localities from this study; dark line, Subtropical Front; light line, Polar Front." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5260968/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

